title: Vixen - Jill Kassidy (Young College Girl Hot Summer) NEW 21 Sept
description:
School is out and Jill has the whole house to herself for the week. She has recently met a hot senior at a party and she can't wait to get him alone. When he comes to her house, they relax at the pool with a few drinks and end up fooling around in the water together. It doesn't take long before they are making out and this leads to much more than Jill could have possibly dreamed of. It seems that this school break is going to be something to remember.
